---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1><span class="gradient-text">ai2rules</span></h1>
			<p>
				A deterministic governance kernel that sits underneath local CLI developer agents 
				(Claude Code, Codex, Aider) and controls what they can perceive, what actions they can represent, 
				and what validated specs may cross into real execution.
			</p>
			<h2>The Flywheel Engine</h2>
			<p>
				This is the central hub for the <strong>Reciprocal-Feeding System</strong>.
				Here, we publish deep-dives, architectural ADRs, and security findings generated by our 
				parallel multi-agent workflow.
			</p>
			<h3>Recent Highlights</h3>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Discovery:</strong> Autonomous radar finding the latest in agent sandboxing.</li>
				<li><strong>Development:</strong> Implementing <code>IntentIR</code> and monotonic taint boundaries.</li>
				<li><strong>Advocacy:</strong> Terminal VHS demos and Google Discover-optimized articles.</li>
			</ul>
			<p>
				<a href="/blog" class="button">Read the Engineering Logs</a>
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
